metadata.name: Hudo Social Club #1
metadata.description: HUDO Social Club is a new social program for onboarding new artists, a place to help and support emergent, talented and new trend artists who want to be part of the Web3 ecosystem. HUDO PFP holders, through HUDO Social Club, will benefit with priority access to new drops, be able to select new artists, access to IRL and online events, exclusive content, gaming and metaverse.
